#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kolf; is a miniature golf game with block graphics and a 2d top-down "
#| "view. Courses are dynamic, and up to 10 people can play at once in "
#| "competition."
msgid ""
"&kolf; is a miniature golf game with 2d top-down view. Courses are dynamic, "
"and up to 10 people can play at once in competition."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; er et miniature-golfspil med blokgrafik og 2-dimensional visning "
"oppefra og nedad. Banerne er dynamiske og indtil 10 mennesker kan spille mod "
"hinanden på én gang."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
