msgstr "Banens navn:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list "
#| "box on the left of this page. &kolf; comes with many built-in courses "
#| "that you can play."
msgid ""
"To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list box "
"on the left of this page. &kolf; comes with many built-in courses that you "
"can play."
msgstr ""
"For at vælge banen som du vil spille, klikkes på den i listefeltet til "
"venstre på siden. &kolf; levereres med mange færdige baner som du kan spille."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
#| "<guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and "
#| "choose the course file in the file dialog."
msgid ""
"To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
"<guibutton>Add…</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and choose "
"the course file in the file dialog."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en bane som du har hentet eller lavet, klikkes på knappen "
"<guibutton>Tilføj...</guibutton> længst nede på siden, og banens fil vælges "
"i filvalgsdialogen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can choose whether or not this game will be played in "
"<guilabel>Strict mode</guilabel>. In strict mode, there is no undo, moving "
"holes, or editing of the course. This mode is generally for competition. "
"Only in strict mode are high scores kept."
msgstr ""
"På denne side kan du vælge om spillet skal spilles i <guilabel>Streng "
"tilstand</guilabel>. I streng tilstand kan du ikke fortryde, flytte huller "
"eller redigere af banen. Denne tilstand er i almindelighed beregnet til  "
"konkurrencer. Topresultat udregnes kun i streng tilstand."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saved Games"
msgstr "Gemte spil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kolf; can keep a history of your rounds that are still in progress and "
#| "save them to disk so you can load them and play them later. Saved games "
#| "include the current hole, names and colors of all players in game, and "
#| "the scores of the players."
msgid ""
"&kolf; can keep a history of your rounds that are still in progress and save "
"them to disk so you can load them and play them later. Saved games include "
"the current hole, names and colors of all players in game, and the scores of "
"the players."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; kan gemme en historik over spillen som stadigvæk er i gang, og gemme "
"dem til disken, så du kan indlæse dem og spille senere. Gemte spil omfatter "
"nuværende hul, navn og farver for alle spiller i spillet, og points for "
"spillerne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Your Game"
msgstr "Gem dit spil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To save your game while still playing, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. If you have "
#| "not saved a game on this game before, you will be prompted for the file "
#| "to save to."
msgid ""
"To save your game while still playing, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. If you "
"have not saved a game on this game before, you will be prompted for the file "
"to save to."
msgstr ""
"For at gemme spillet mens det stadigvæk er gang, vælges "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Spil</guimenu><guimenuitem>Gem spil</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Hvis du ikke har gemt spillet for denne omgang tidligere, "
"bliver du spurgt om filen det skal gemmes til."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading Your Game"
msgstr "Indlæs et spil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To load the game that you saved, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Load Saved Game...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. You "
#| "can then choose the saved game to open."
msgid ""
"To load the game that you saved, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. You can "
"then choose the saved game to open."
msgstr ""
"For at indlæse spillet du gemte, vælges <menuchoice><guimenu>Spil</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Indlæs gemt spil...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Du kan "
"så vælge det gemte spil som skal åbnes."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practicing"
msgstr "Øve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a few features that make practicing your golf easier. These "
"features are not enabled during strict mode."
msgstr ""
"Der er nogle funktioner som gør det lettere at øve sig i golfspillet. Disse "
"funktioner er ikke aktiverede i streng tilstand."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo"
msgstr "Fortryd"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To undo a bad shot, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo Shot</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"To undo a bad shot, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Undo Shot</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"For at fortryde et dårligt slag, vælges <menuchoice><guimenu>Hul</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Fortryd slag</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Holes"
msgstr "Skift hul"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu contains many menu items for switching to "
"different holes that are quite self explanatory. See the <link linkend=\"go-"
"menu\"><guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu reference</link>."
msgstr ""
"Menuen <guimenu>Kør</guimenu> indeholder mange menupunkter til at skifte "
"mellem forskellige huller som er helt selvforklarende. Se <link linkend=\"go-"
"menu\">menupunktet</link> for <guimenu>Kør</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Putting Options"
msgstr "Putningsvalgmuligheder"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kolf; has a few ways to putt. The basic putting method is <link linkend="
#| "\"hitting\">described above</link>."
msgid ""
"&kolf; has a few ways to putt. The basic putting method is <link linkend="
"\"hitting\">described above</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; har nogle forskellige måde at putte. Den grundlæggende putningsmetode "
"<link linkend=\"hitting\">beskrives ovenfor</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse is enabled by default. This means that whenever the mouse is "
"moved, the putter aligns to the line between the mouse and ball."
msgstr ""
"Musen er normalt aktiveret. Det betyder at så snart musen flyttes, så "
"justeres putteren til linjen mellem musen og bolden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you prefer to only use the keyboard and arrow keys, you can disable "
#| "mouse putting by unchecking <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"If you prefer to only use the keyboard and arrow keys, you can disable mouse "
"putting by unchecking the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du foretrækker kun at bruge tastaturet og pilene, kan du lukke af for "
"museputning ved at afmarkere <menuchoice><guimenu>Indstillinger</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Aktivér mus for at flytte putter</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Putting"
msgstr "Avanceret putning"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Advanced putting can be enabled by checking "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable Advanced "
#| "Putting</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This putting mode is slightly more "
#| "challenging than the regular click-and-hold mode, and can be used with "
#| "either the mouse or keyboard."
msgid ""
"Advanced putting can be enabled by checking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Advanced "
"Putting</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This putting mode is slightly "
"more challenging than the regular click-and-hold mode, and can be used with "
"either the mouse or keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Avanceret putning kan aktiveres ved at markere "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Indstillinger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Aktivér avanceret "
"putning</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Denne putningstilstand er noget sværere "
"end den almindelige <quote>klik og hold</quote> tilstand, og kan enten "
"bruges med musen eller tastaturet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "To putt in this mode:"
msgstr "For at putte i denne tilstand:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key once to begin the "
#| "swing. The putting indicator will appear, and the strength gauge will "
#| "start filling up with a color, which changes as the gauge fills up."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key once to begin the swing. The putting "
"indicator will appear, and the strength gauge will start filling up with a "
"color, which changes as the gauge fills up."
msgstr ""
"Klik eller tryk på tasten <keycap>Nedad pil</keycap> en gang for at begynde "
"svinget. Putningsindikatoren vises, og styrkemåleren begynder at fyldes op "
"med en farve, som ændres mens måleren fyldes."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key when the strength "
#| "gauge has filled up the amount that you want. The farther around the "
#| "circle the strength gauge has filled up, the stronger the putt will be. "
#| "It takes practice to be able to get the correct strength on putts."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key when the strength gauge has filled up "
"the amount that you want. The farther around the circle the strength gauge "
"has filled up, the stronger the putt will be. It takes practice to be able "
"to get the correct strength on putts."
msgstr ""
"Klik eller tryk på tasten <keycap>Nedad pil</keycap> når styrkemåleren er "
"fyldt så meget op som du vil. Jo længere styrkemåleren fyldes rundt i "
"cirkelen, desto stærkere bliver putten. Der kræves øvelse for at få den "
"rigtige styrke for puttene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After this, the color in the putting indicator will start to wind down back "
"to where it started."
msgstr ""
"Derefter, begynder farven i putningsindikatoren at gå tilbage til hvor den "
"begyndte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key again when the "
#| "strength-indicator is as close as possible to the center line of the "
#| "putting indicator."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key again when the strength-indicator is as "
"close as possible to the center line of the putting indicator."
msgstr ""
"Klik eller tryk på tasten <keycap>Nedad pil</keycap> igen, når styrkemåleren "
"er så nær som muligt ved putningsindikatornes centrumlinje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The closer the final click (or key press) is, the more true the putt is to "
"the original line."
msgstr ""
"Jo nærmere det endelige klik (eller tastetrykket) er, desto tættere bliver "
"putten ved den oprindelige linje."

